              <ul> A <strong>standard</strong> track is a 400m track generally found at most high schools and colleges.</ul>
              <br>
              <ul> A <strong>non-standard</strong> track might be tracks found at middle schools or inside government parks.</ul>
               <!--popup's close button-->
              <button class="close">Close</button>    
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="control">
            <input class="input is-focused" type="text" placeholder="Street Address" id="address">
